# Franky Configuration - LOCAL TESTING (Python only, no hardware)
#
# Use this preset for testing on your Mac without ESP32/MQTT/Camera
# Just speakers and microphone on your computer
#
# Usage: cp .env.example.local .env

# ============================================================
# REQUIRED: OpenAI API
# ============================================================
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-YOUR_API_KEY_HERE

# ============================================================
# OPTIONAL: Camera (disabled for local testing)
# ============================================================
# Leave commented out or set to empty to disable camera
# CAMERA_RTSP_STREAM=

# ============================================================
# OPTIONAL: ESP32 (disabled for local testing)
# ============================================================
# Leave commented out to skip ESP32
# ESP32_IP=

# ============================================================
# OPTIONAL: MQTT (disabled for local testing)
# ============================================================
# Leave commented out to skip MQTT
# MQTT_SERVER=
# MQTT_PORT=1883

# ============================================================
# TESTING NOTES
# ============================================================
# Run with: python3 voice_bot_realtime_speakers.py
#
# Features available:
# - ✅ Voice conversation via OpenAI
# - ✅ Mac microphone input
# - ✅ Mac speaker output
# - ✅ Audio effects (reverb, pitch shift)
# - ✅ Background music playback
# - ❌ Camera vision (no camera)
# - ❌ Jaw movement (no hardware)
# - ❌ LED eyes (no hardware)
